                            <comment id="13398737" author="lucasjosh" created="Thu, 21 Jun 2012 18:48:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue is in the creation of the prefix variable where an additional dot is added. The SPELLCHECK_PREFIX variable already includes the dot.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
